ype":"example","text":"B：I swear I've told you all I know.（我发誓已经把知道的都告诉你"},{"type":"text","text":"了。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：“What are you doing there?” she inquired. （“你在那里做什"},{"type":"text","text":"么？”她问道。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：“Take care of the children's daily life.” Amy answered. （“照顾孩"},{"type":"text","text":"子们的日常生活起居。”埃米回答道。）"}]},{"number":698,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"Chapter7 喜怒哀乐听你说"}]}]}